search_results.title: Korpiklaani
search_results.snippet: Korpiklaani (Finnish for The Backwoods Clan) is a Finnish folk metal band from Lahti that was formerly known as Shamaani Duo and Shaman.

search_results.title: Korpiklaani - Biography
search_results.snippet: Korpiklaani (or "Forest Clan") emerged out of the ashes of Shaman, when the band opted to change its name, along with its musical and lyrical expression.
